fr.inrialpes.exmo.align.impl.eval

Class SemPRecEvaluator

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inrialpes.exmo.align.impl.BasicEvaluator

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Evaluator

    public class SemPRecEvaluator
extends PRecEvaluator
implements Evaluator
    Evaluate proximity between two alignments. This function implements Precision/Recall. The first alignment is thus the expected one.
